    {
      "@id": "asbval:assertion/card/task_001/scope_drift",
      "@type": "asbval:ScopeDriftAssertion",
      "asbval:drift_notes": [
        "The candidate card describes a specific function 'buildExperiment' that constructs SummarizedExperiment objects. The paper does not mention this function by name or describe SummarizedExperiment object construction.",
        "The paper focuses on quality control and batch correction workflows in mzQuality, not on internal data structure implementation details like SummarizedExperiment construction.",
        "The card appears to describe an internal implementation detail or helper function that may exist in the mzQuality R package but is not documented or discussed in this paper.",
