      "asbval:note": "Paper confirms ratio computation (compound/IS) is performed by mzQuality, but does NOT mention SummarizedExperiment objects, buildExperiment function, or secondary assay slots. The card claims verification of ratio computation within a SummarizedExperiment data structure; the paper describes the mathematical operation but not the Bioconductor object framework. This is a partial match: the function (ratio computation) exists, but the claimed implementation context (SummarizedExperiment) is not mentioned in the passages.",
