      "asbval:evidence_quote": "mzQuality also provides suggestions for alternative ISs, but the user must check the compatibility of the IS with the compound. These suggestions are based on calculations that evaluate all compound and IS combinations to determine which combination gives the best RSDqc after batch correction.",
      "asbval:note": "Paper confirms mzQuality evaluates IS combinations and calculates RSDqc to suggest optimal ISs. However, the paper does NOT describe an exhaustive search across ALL internal standard candidates per compound. Instead, mzQuality provides suggestions based on evaluating combinations, but the user must validate compatibility. The framing of 'exhaustively calculating RSDQC across all internal standard candidates' overstates the automation; the paper indicates suggestions are provided but user validation is required.",
