      "asbval:target_claim_field": "research_question",
      "asbval:target_claim_text": "Batch-correct compound/internal-standard ratios in metabolomics LC-MS/MS data using pooled study quality control (SQC) samples as anchors. This corrects for systematic drift and matrix effects across injection sequences while preserving biological signal.",
