      "asbval:note": "mzQuality and GitHub repo confirmed. However, paper does not name functions 'readData' or 'buildExperiment', nor does it mention SummarizedExperiment construction. Paper describes validation and data processing but does not explicitly document these function names or SummarizedExperiment output.",
