      "asbval:note": "Paper describes mzQuality as an R-Shiny app for QC assessment and correction, not as a function that constructs SummarizedExperiment objects. The paper does not mention SummarizedExperiment class or a buildExperiment function. The card claims a specific data structure transformation (to SummarizedExperiment) that is not documented in the paper. The paper focuses on QC workflows, not object construction.",
